@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home page";
}


<section class="row" id="row1">
    <div class="sectionHeader">
        <h2>Custom Office Desks</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="articleImage">
        <img src="~/images/oak.jpg" alt="Oak desktop" />
    </div>
    <div class="articleText">
        <p>We create <b>amazing</b>, custom desks for both home and corporate offices. Our woodworkers have years of experience and are able to pick the best wood for your projects.</p>
        <p>Our desks are made with a metal frame and a wood top, and we can customize the shape and size of the desk to your specifications.</p>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="row border-top" id="row2">
    <div class="sectionHeader">
        <h2>Why Mega Desk</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="articleText">
        <p><b>Quality</b> is always our priority. Every desk is hand made to the exact desired dimensions. All of our material comes from surrounding local business with the finest quality. Our desks are made to last. Our desks will stand the test to times while providing you with the comfort you need.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="articleImage">
        <img src="~/images/desktop2.jpg" alt="desk image" />
    </div>
</section>
<section class="row border-top" id="row3">
    <div class="sectionHeader">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="articleImage">
        <img src="~/images/man-working.jpg" alt="Oak desktop" />
    </div>
    <div class="articleText">
        <p>We started our business in 2020, but collectively we have 10+ years of experience designing and building custom desks.</p> 
        <p>Our team has a variety of skills that will ensure that your desk is <b>unique</b>. Our passion is making desks that last a life time. </p>
    </div>
</section>

